────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Any product, game, application, or service that uses, derives from, or is
substantially built upon this engine or its architecture must include a visible
credit in one or more of the following locations:

  - The product's in-game credits screen or about page
  - The product's public-facing README or documentation
  - The product's store page, landing page, or website

The credit must read, at minimum:

  "Engine architecture based on work by Ocean Bennett
   (https://github.com/oceanbbennett/SINGLE-PLAYER-AI-MUD)"

  or an equivalent that names Ocean Bennett and links to this repository.

This requirement applies regardless of how substantially the code was modified.
